Set the mode for all charts of all users in this server. While this is set any user configuration will be overridden.
		The possible values for the chart mode are the following:
			**Image**: Using the standard image format
			**Image-info**: Adds additional info to better identify the user of the chart
			**Image-aside**: Shows titles on the side of the chart
			**Image-aside-info**: Image Info and Aside Together
			**List**: Shows it on a embed
			**Pie**: Shows using a pie chart
			**Clear**: Sets the default mode

			**Random**: Uses a random colour
			**Role**: Uses the color of your role in a server
